### MARBLE MANIA AUTOSPLITTER!!!
- A basic Marble Mania autosplitter for speedrunning.
- Contains timer for all 7 tracks + tutorial.
- Unfortunately, it is buggy as hell (as I dont really know how 2 use cheat engine).
- Can start, but cant split and reset. You have to do those manually.
- Speedrun page (https://www.speedrun.com/Marble_Mania)

### REQUIREMENTS
- Livesplit (http://livesplit.org/downloads/)
- Marble Mania v2.1.1 (https://gamejolt.com/games/MarbleMania/287568)
- Autosplitter activated (or download the .asl and add it to scriptable auto splitter)
- **MAKE SURE THE TIMING METHOD IS SET TO "GAME TIME"!**
